                        <h2 class="sec-hd color reveal reveal-left delay-1">People Behind the Purpose</h2>
                        <p class="para-color reveal reveal-left delay-2">We are a team driven by purpose, creativity, and respect for
                            authors, focused on building meaningful publishing experiences for both new and experienced
                            authors worldwide.</p>

                        <div class="btn-container d-flex align-items-center gap-3 reveal reveal-left delay-3">
